description:
This event is being hosted by GDG London. To RSVP, please visit their event page at: https://gdg.community.dev/events/details/google-gdg-london-presents-chrome-dev-summit-extended-uk-ireland/#/

2020 has been a very unique year. We need to stay connected, informed and to support each other more than ever before.

The Web plays a special role here, and through Chrome Dev Summit Extended, we want to take a moment to allow web developers to come together, share their stories and acknowledge the latest in the platform and tools.

The event will include talks on helpful features and tooling around Web Vitals, privacy, modern UX and more.

This event is being hosted by GDG London. To RSVP, please visit their event page at: https://gdg.community.dev/events/details/google-gdg-london-presents-chrome-dev-summit-extended-uk-ireland/#/
title: Chrome Dev Summit Extended UK & Ireland
